<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
<title>Gewara-帮助页面</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${staticPath}css/gewara.css?n=global,sns,new_movie,index,help&v=$VmUtils.jsVersion"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${staticPath}styles/slider.css?v=$VmUtils.jsVersion"/>
<script type="text/javascript" src="${staticPath}scripts/mootools.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="${staticPath}scripts/gewara.js?n=gewara-util,page,noobSlide,slimbox&v=$VmUtils.jsVersion"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="head">
		#set($cfgHeader='header')#parse('include/navigation.vm')
</div>
<div id='panel'>
	<div class="hp"><h1>取票帮助中心</h1></div>
	<input type="hidden" id="footertag" value="stpe"/>
	<div class='helpleft'>
		#parse('footer/help/help_left.vm')
	</div>
	<div class='helpright'>
		<div class="helpcontent">
			<div class="title">格瓦拉电影票自助取票流程</div>
			<div class="mt10"><strong>1、查看您的取票短信</strong></div>
			<div style="padding-left:30px;margin-top:20px;"><a href="/service/help/images/stpe1.jpg" rel="lightbox[galerie]" target="_blank"><img src="/service/help/images/stpe1.jpg" class="img2" alt="取票第一步" width="600"/></a></div>
			<div class="mt10"><strong>2、	输入取票短信中的八位“取票密码”，并点击确认</strong></div>
			<div style="padding-left:30px;margin-top:20px;"><a href="/service/help/images/stpe2.jpg" rel="lightbox[galerie]" target="_blank"><img src="/service/help/images/stpe2.jpg" class="img2" alt="取票第二步" width="600"/></a></div>
			<div class="mt10"><strong>3、	核对您的购票信息，确认无误后点击“确认”</strong></div>
			<div style="padding-left:30px;margin-top:20px;"><a href="/service/help/images/stpe3.jpg" rel="lightbox[galerie]" target="_blank"><img src="/service/help/images/stpe3.jpg" class="img2" alt="取票第三步" width="600"/></a></div>
			<div class="mt10"><strong>4、	在指示箭头指示的取票口取票</strong></div>
			<div style="padding-left:30px;margin-top:20px;"><a href="/service/help/images/stpe4.jpg" rel="lightbox[galerie]" target="_blank"><img src="/service/help/images/stpe4.jpg" class="img2" alt="取票第四步" width="600"/></a></div>
			<div class="mt20"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id='height0'></div>
</div>
<div id="footer">#parse('include/bottom.vm')</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
window.addEvent('domready', function(){
	(function(){$($('footertag').value).addClass("pointer");}).delay(500);
	Slimbox.scanPage();
});
</script>
</body>
</html>